body_html:
As a reference, I profiled the same program with NVIDIA Visual Profiler. It shows that each matrix multiplication (MatMul_[0-9]) takes around 65-75ms.

In comparison, tfprof doubles the amount of runtime of MatMul_[0-4] while counting that of MatMul_[5-9] almost as zero.

body:
As a reference, I profiled the same program with NVIDIA Visual Profiler. It shows that each matrix multiplication (MatMul_[0-9]) takes around 65-75ms.

In comparison, tfprof doubles the amount of runtime of MatMul_[0-4] while counting that of MatMul_[5-9] almost as zero.
